    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      277.63,
      108.11,
      337.4,
      121.39
    ],
    "text": "Judgement",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      143.86,
      143.3,
      157.14
    ],
    "text": "Introduction",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      179.36,
      543.23,
      192.64
    ],
    "text": "The Petitioner claims that he is entitled to have a certificate of title issued under the Title",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      206.2,
      543.05,
      220.42
    ],
    "text": "Registration Act, No. 21 of 1998, and that the 1st to 3rd Respondents have failed to issue the said",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.0,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      234.64,
      543.09,
      247.92
    ],
    "text": "certificate. Therefore, he has instituted the above-styled application seeking the intervention of this",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      262.14,
      105.3,
      275.42
    ],
    "text": "Court.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      300.97,
      543.14,
      315.19
    ],
    "text": "After the issuance of notice, the 1st to 4th Respondents have filed their respective Objections and",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.0,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      329.41,
      542.74,
      342.69
    ],
    "text": "denied that the Petitioner has established any right to the land claimed by him. They state that the",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      356.24,
      543.22,
      370.46
    ],
    "text": "land claimed by the Petitioner is different from that claimed by the 5th Respondent, and that the",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.0,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      383.74,
      543.06,
      397.96
    ],
    "text": "rights have already been established by the 5th Respondent; therefore, seek a dismissal of this",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.0,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      412.18,
      134.8,
      425.46
    ],
    "text": "Application.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      451.96,
      543.02,
      465.24
    ],
    "text": "Thereafter, this matter was argued before me on 17.12.2025, and the following arguments were",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      479.46,
      307.13,
      492.74
    ],
    "text": "advanced by the counsel; hence, this judgement.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      518.98,
      132.3,
      532.26
    ],
    "text": "Arguments",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      554.73,
      542.91,
      568.01
    ],
    "text": "The first argument of Dr. Abeyaratne is that the Respondents failed to hold an inquiry after",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      582.26,
      542.83,
      595.54
    ],
    "text": "receiving P13, P14, and P15. Therefore, he argued that since there was no inquiry, the Petitioner",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      610.01,
      456.95,
      623.29
    ],
    "text": "was not given a hearing; as such, the rules of natural justice have been violated.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      645.51,
      542.91,
      658.79
    ],
    "text": "The next contention of the Dr. Abeyrathna is that the evidence placed by the Petitioner was not",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      673.03,
      400.67,
      686.31
    ],
    "text": "considered by the Respondents; therefore, a Writ of Mandamus lies.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-ItalicMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      728.03,
      312.13,
      756.34
    ],
    "text": "4",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      72.59,
      543.23,
      85.87
    ],
    "text": "On the other hand, Mr. Jayasuriya argued that there is no nexus or proof to establish P5 and P5(a).",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      100.09,
      433.17,
      113.37
    ],
    "text": "In addition to that, no nexus between P5 and P8 has ever been established.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      135.86,
      543.22,
      149.14
    ],
    "text": "Further, he argued that there is a delay from 2012 to 2016 in what the Petitioner sought to pursue,",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      163.36,
      450.43,
      176.64
    ],
    "text": "and therefore, the Petitioner has not established or explained the undue delay.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      199.14,
      543.09,
      212.42
    ],
    "text": "He further argued that Section 59 of the Title Registration Act does not apply to the situation, and",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      226.64,
      218.85,
      239.92
    ],
    "text": "the Court cannot go into that.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      262.14,
      542.6,
      275.42
    ],
    "text": "Finally, he argued that the relief sought by the Petitioner cannot be granted since they are not",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      289.91,
      110.8,
      303.19
    ],
    "text": "certain.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      325.41,
      543.07,
      338.69
    ],
    "text": "Further countering the arguments advanced on behalf of the Petitioner, Mr. Jayasuriya contended",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      353.18,
      542.77,
      366.46
    ],
    "text": "that 1R5 establishes that there had been an inquiry; therefore, the Petitioner cannot be heard",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      380.68,
      242.35,
      393.96
    ],
    "text": "claiming that there was no inquiry.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      416.18,
      406.92,
      429.46
    ],
    "text": "In this case, I will first advert to the facts as presented in the Petition.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      451.96,
      151.3,
      465.24
    ],
    "text": "Factual matrix",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      487.46,
      543.2,
      500.74
    ],
